2:02:00.000 --> 2:02:01.500
Pray for me.

2:02:44.166 --> 2:02:46.166
Come, children! Quickly!

2:02:47.125 --> 2:02:48.291
Join the boat!

2:02:49.041 --> 2:02:50.250
We leave now!

2:02:59.500 --> 2:03:01.416
[high-pitched shrieking]

2:04:59.750 --> 2:05:01.791
